sections.content:
This code has a hidden bug:
```javascript
let userInput = "10";  // From a form (always a string)
let result = userInput + 5;
console.log(result);   // "105" — NOT 15!
```

The fix: Always convert user input to a number first:
```javascript
let userInput = "10";
let result = Number(userInput) + 5;
console.log(result);   // 15 ✅
```

This bug has caused countless hours of debugging for beginners. Always be aware of your data types!

