For accessible forms, add `aria-invalid` and `aria-describedby` attributes:
```javascript
function updateFieldUI(input, errorSpan, error) {
  input.setAttribute('aria-invalid', !!error);
  input.classList.toggle('invalid', !!error);
  input.classList.toggle('valid', !error);
  errorSpan.textContent = error || '';
  errorSpan.setAttribute('role', 'alert'); // Screen readers announce this
}
```
Also ensure your error messages are specific: 'Password must be at least 8 characters' is better than just 'Invalid password'. Screen reader users rely on these messages.

