// Now what if we need a SwimmingCat?
// We'd have to duplicate the swim logic!
// Or create weird hierarchies like SwimmingAnimal...
// What about a FlyingSwimmingDog? 😱

// This is called the "gorilla-banana problem":
// "I wanted a banana, but I got a gorilla holding the banana
//  and the entire jungle." — Joe Armstrong
//
// When you inherit, you get EVERYTHING from the parent chain,
